 / A wood burning stove also sits in the sitting room. The kitchen is located in the original part of the house where the rafters are exposed to open up the space. The kitchen is a mixture of timber counters and stainless steel fixtures. A mezzanine also sits in this part of the house and is accessed by steep steps perhaps perfect for a home office. The home is available through Charles McCarthy Auctioneers for €685,000 Online Editors 
